                ### Use Azure's built-in editor to create and deploy the HTML file:

                  <!DOCTYPE html>
                  <html lang="en">
                  <head>
                      <meta charset="UTF-8">
                      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
                      <title>Welcome</title>

                  </head>
                  <body>
                      <h1>Welcome to Azure Web App!</h1>
                  </body>
                  </html>



